    "To manage Offshore’s iCloud storage, open the iOS Settings app and go to:\nApple ID → iCloud → Storage → Offshore Budgeting" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "لإدارة مساحة تخزين iCloud الخاصة بـ Offshore، افتح تطبيق إعدادات iOS وانتقل إلى:\nمعرف Apple → iCloud → التخزين → ميزانية Offshore"
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Um den iCloud-Speicher von Offshore zu verwalten, öffnen Sie die iOS-Einstellungen-App und gehen Sie zu:\nApple-ID → iCloud → Speicher → Offshore Budgetierung"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para administrar el almacenamiento de iCloud de Offshore, abre la app Ajustes de iOS y ve a:\nApple ID → iCloud → Almacenamiento → Offshore Budgeting"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To manage Offshore’s iCloud storage, open the iOS Réglages app and go to:\nApple ID → iCloud → Storage → Offshore Budgeting"
